499
00:39:31,046 --> 00:39:31,307
Rym: disk.".

500
00:39:31,931 --> 00:39:37,229
Rym: And it was like, it is hard to express how fucking excited we all were to do this.

501
00:39:38,231 --> 00:39:55,590
