00:46:27,392 --> 00:46:30,729
Scott: It doesn't need to connect to anything with a cable other than power, right?

583
00:46:30,930 --> 00:46:47,050
Scott: You fill it up with ink and paper and now you can scan, print, fax, et cetera, copy, and you can send things from your phone or literally any device on your whole home network to it to print or scan something on it and send that to any device, right?

584
00:46:47,170 --> 00:46:51,190
Scott: It's like you could put a piece of paper, get the piece of paper on a phone, tablet, whatever.

