00:57:41,931 --> 00:57:42,154
Scott: Yep.

723
00:57:43,285 --> 00:57:43,648
Scott: There you go.

724
00:57:44,650 --> 00:57:47,018
Rym: And maybe I do this every couple months.

725
00:57:47,038 --> 00:57:50,250
Rym: I have like one thing that I scan because I want to throw away the piece of paper.

726
00:57:50,831 --> 00:57:51,175
Rym: That's it.

727
00:57:51,397 --> 00:57:52,590
Rym: That's the only reason I have a scanner.

